<para>
  This menu contains commands for selecting pixels in a &micro;. Each
  &micro; has one current pixel selection state and a stack of past
  selections, which are accessible through the <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.PixelSelection.Undo"><command>Undo</command></link>
  and <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.PixelSelection.Redo"><command>Redo</command></link>
  commands.
</para>
<para>
  Some commands in this menu create selections
  (<foreignphrase>e.g</foreignphrase>, <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.PixelSelection.Select_Group"><command>Select
  Group</command></link>) and some modify the existing selection
  (<foreignphrase>e.g</foreignphrase>, <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.PixelSelection.Despeckle"><command>Despeckle</command></link>.
  Tools for creating and modifying selections via mouse clicks in a
  <link linkend="Chapter-Graphics">Graphics</link> window may be found
  in the <link linkend="Section-Graphics-PixelSelection">Pixel
  Selection</link> toolbox.
</para>

